Delivery API (Express + TypeScript + Mongoose)

A production-ready REST API for a food delivery platform built with Node.js, Express, TypeScript, and MongoDB (Mongoose). It covers user authentication, restaurants, products, orders with transactional order items, and reviews. Includes JWT auth, role-based access control, request validation, and robust error handling.

âœ¨ Features

Auth: Register/Login with JWT

RBAC: Roles customer, driver, restaurant

Data Models: Users, Drivers, Restaurants, Products, Orders, OrderItems, Reviews

Transactions: Atomic order creation with order items

Validation: express-validator

Security: helmet, CORS, sanitised JSON parsing

Logging: morgan

TypeScript: Strict types & ES Modules

